Palʊla Julie Akofa Akoussah kɛ ɖomaɣ fenaɣ 12 wiye pɩnaɣ 1950 kɛ Ceviye tɛtʊ taa, Togo ɛjaɖɛ taa. Payɣ-ɩ nabʊyʊ taa yem se Julie, Mamy yaa Akofa. Ɖooo ɛ-pɩcatʊ kɛ ɛkpaɣ-ɛtɩ kpem nɛ ɛcɛlɩ hendu teu. Weyi ɛɛkɩla-ɩ kɛdɩnaʊ hendu teʊ taa yɔ, ɛnʊ Bella Bello. 

Pɩla mbʊ lɛ e-hendu sakɩyɛ taa ɛnʊ ɛwɛɛ ɛɖɛyʊ.
Julie Akofa Akoussah kɛna Togo ɛjaɖɛ taa hendu teyu sɔsɔ nɔɔyʊ nɛ ɛsɩ Parii tɛtʊ taa, Fransɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa, kɛ  pɩya wiye, ɖomaɣ fenaɣ kɩyakʊ 25 wiye pɩnaɣ 2007. Ɛsɩbʊ yɔ ɛɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 57. Ɛ-sɩm mbʊ TVT sʊsɩna-tʊ tɛʊ kɩfemuu cɩla wiye. 

Ɛ-sɩm takayaɣ kɛna posusa kɔ-tɔm TVT taa wɩsɩ taa. Julie Akofa Akoussah ɛnɛ ɛsʊwaɣ ɛ-pɩnzɩ 40 kɛ ɛpaɣzɩɣ hendu teu yɔ pɩ- kasanʊ nɛ kʊtɔŋ nakʊyʊ tii ɛ-yɔɔ kpiɖi nɛ kpaagbaa mbʊ yɔ pɛɖɛna-ɩ Fransɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa se tɛtɛ ɛsɔ ɛwɛɛ kɔyɔ, paalɛɣ-ɩ nɛ pɛlakɩ pɩɩcɔʊ mbʊ yɔ.

